The American president, Donald Trump, on Friday said the US is working closely with China to combat corona virus scourge because has a good understanding of the virus. Trump, who said he had a conversation with Chinese president, made this statement via his official twitter page on Friday. He said, “Just finished a very good conversation with President Xi Jinping of China. Discussed in great detail the CoronaVirus that is ravaging large parts of our Planet. “China has been through much & has developed a strong understanding of the Virus. We are working closely together. Much respect!” According to worldometer.com, America has recorded new 177 cases and 1301 deaths, while China has recorded 55 new cases and 3292 deaths.